AGENTS.md

# ── Claude Code Data Recovery Kit ──────────────────────────────────────
# Collected backups contain full transcripts, pasted secrets and LIVE OAuth
# tokens. They must NEVER be committed. Local/dry-run output lands here; only
# the explanatory README is tracked.
claude-data-recovery/outputs/*
!claude-data-recovery/outputs/README.md
# NOTE: the built collector .exe is the SHIPPED PRODUCT — it must travel with
# the repo so people can grab & run it. The generic `dist/` rule above would
# hide it, so re-include its dist dir and the exe explicitly.
!claude-data-recovery/tool/dist/
!claude-data-recovery/tool/dist/ClaudeBackup.exe
# Safety net: never commit a collected backup tree, wherever it lands.
claude-backup/
__SECRETS__/


#Ignore vscode AI rules
.github\instructions\codacy.instructions.md
